    "C. LLM for Autonomous DrivingThe integration of LLMs into autonomous driving systems signified a transformative leap towards embedding humanlike intelligence for enhanced decision-making and interaction capabilities.",
    "emphasized the role of LLMs as cognitive agents in autonomous driving systems, highlighting their capacity to integrate human-like intelligence across various functions such as perception, prediction, and planning [32].",
